        </h2></div></div><div class="one-double-info__right"><div
    id="block-40023"
    class="one-generic-info block one-generic-info--content-size-Default"
    ><div
                class="one-generic-into__content one-generic-info__content--color-black"
                data-fx-child><p></p><h3>Innoveren en groeien doen we graag samen. Daarbij kijken we verder dan jouw vraagstuk van nu. We blijven waarde toevoegen, nu en in de toekomst.&nbsp;Samen realiseren we krachtige oplossingen die&nbsp;bijdragen aan jouw succes.</h3><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><style>
                        
                                #section-21561 {
            background-color: var(--color-background-green1);
        }
        
        
                
        
            </style><section id="section-21561"    
    class="one-section section  one-resp-p-t-sm one-resp-p-b-sm one-section--height-min-md one-section--border-bottom-lg-white one-section--bg-green1 one-section--overflow-x-clip"><div class="one-section__container one-container one-location-none sm:one-location-none md:one-location md:one-location-west lg:one-location lg:one-location-west one-container--content"><div class="one-section__content  "><header id="block-40008" class="block one-section-header"><div
    class="one-section-header__titles-wrapper one-u-m-b-32"
    ><h2 class="one-section-header__title one-u-m-b-0 one-section-header__title--color-white one-section-header__title--lg">Bekijk hier onze recente artikelen    </h2><p class="one-section-header__subtitle one-u-m-t-16 one-u-m-b-0 one-section-header__subtitle--color-white">
            Wil je meer lezen? Ga naar <a href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/">ons werk</a> voor alle artikelen, klantverhalen en projectcases.
        </p></div></header><div class="one-grid1"><div class="one-grid1__cell"><div id="block-40014" class="one-card1 one-panel block content--full-height one-u-color-base one-card1--has-subtitle one-panel--shadow one-panel--border"
    ><style>
            #block-40014-card-hero-image .one-card-hero-image__image {
            background-image: url('https://i.tb-content.net/cms/1d38cb/signetbreedband_server_1.png');
        }
    
    </style><figure
    class="one-card-hero-image one-card-hero-image--lg one-card-hero-image--for-panel"
    role="img"
    id="block-40014-card-hero-image" aria-hidden="true"><a
                        href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/uptimegarantie/"
                        tabindex="-1"
                            class="one-card-hero-image__image one-card-hero-image__scalable"
    

                                                ><span class="one-u-sr-only">Artikel</span></a><div class="one-btn one-btn--primary one-btn--square one-btn--sm one-card-hero-image__continue-button"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="svg-pictogram svg-pictogram--arrow-right-straight" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="m50 100 50-50L50 0 39.879 9.97l32.78 32.93H0v14.2h72.659l-32.78 32.779z" fill-rule="evenodd"/></svg></div></figure><div class="one-card1__wrapper"><div class="one-card1__top"><div id="block-40014_one-media-header" class="one-media-header one-card1__header one-u-m-b-8 one-media-header--icon-sm one-media-header--title-sm one-media-header--title-normal one-media-header--subtitle-md"><div class="one-media-header__body"><header><a
                            href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/uptimegarantie/"
                            class="one-media-header__heading-link"

                            
                            
                                                    ><h4 class="one-media-header__title one-media-header__title--color-black"><h3>Artikel</h3></h4></a><div class="one-media-header__subtitle one-u-m-b-0"><h2>Uptime garantie - een noodzakelijke belofte</h2></div></header></div></div><div class="one-card1__content"><p>In een wereld waarin digitale processen 24/7 moeten draaien, kan een verschil van een paar procent in uptime het verschil betekenen tussen ongemak en bedrijfsschade. In dit artikel lees je wat uptime garanties &eacute;cht betekenen, waarom 99,97% zoveel impact heeft, en hoe je als IT-manager voorbereid blijft met de juiste keuzes in infrastructuur, SLA&rsquo;s en monitoring.&nbsp;Ontdek hoe signetbreedband uptime niet alleen belooft, maar waarmaakt.</p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div class="one-card1__link"><a class="one-btn one-btn--link one-btn--bare one-btn--icon one-btn--icon-before one-u-text-left" href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/uptimegarantie/" aria-disabled="false"><span class="one-btn__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="svg-pictogram svg-pictogram--arrow-right" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="M31 .4L19.4 12l38 38-38 38L31 99.6 80.6 50 31 .4zm0 0"/></svg></span><span class="one-btn__label">Lees meer</span></a></div></div></div></div><div class="one-grid1__cell"><div id="block-40011" class="one-card1 one-panel block content--full-height one-u-color-base one-card1--has-subtitle one-panel--shadow one-panel--border"
    ><style>
            #block-40011-card-hero-image .one-card-hero-image__image {
            background-image: url('https://i.tb-content.net/cms/1d38cb/2024-overig/peterenjosja.jpg');
        }
    
    </style><figure
    class="one-card-hero-image one-card-hero-image--lg one-card-hero-image--for-panel"
    role="img"
    id="block-40011-card-hero-image" aria-hidden="true"><a
                        href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/optical-transport-network/"
                        tabindex="-1"
                            class="one-card-hero-image__image one-card-hero-image__scalable"
    

                                                ><span class="one-u-sr-only">Artikel</span></a><div class="one-btn one-btn--primary one-btn--square one-btn--sm one-card-hero-image__continue-button"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="svg-pictogram svg-pictogram--arrow-right-straight" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="m50 100 50-50L50 0 39.879 9.97l32.78 32.93H0v14.2h72.659l-32.78 32.779z" fill-rule="evenodd"/></svg></div></figure><div class="one-card1__wrapper"><div class="one-card1__top"><div id="block-40011_one-media-header" class="one-media-header one-card1__header one-u-m-b-8 one-media-header--icon-sm one-media-header--title-sm one-media-header--title-normal one-media-header--subtitle-md"><div class="one-media-header__body"><header><a
                            href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/optical-transport-network/"
                            class="one-media-header__heading-link"

                            
                            
                                                    ><h4 class="one-media-header__title one-media-header__title--color-black"><h3>Artikel</h3></h4></a><div class="one-media-header__subtitle one-u-m-b-0"><h2>Vernieuwd Optical Transport Network (OTN) in Oost-Nederland</h2></div></header></div></div><div class="one-card1__content">
                    			Ons Optical Transport Network (OTN) in Oost-Nederland is vernieuwd! Dit betekent snellere, veiligere en flexibelere verbindingen met hogere capaciteit en minder latency. Bedrijven profiteren van schaalbare netwerken, verbeterde redundantie en geautomatiseerd beheer. Ook hebben we onze infrastructuur gestandaardiseerd met high-quality Nokia-apparatuur. Wat betekent dit voor jouw bedrijf? Lees hoe onze vernieuwde OTN-infrastructuur jouw connectiviteit naar een hoger niveau tilt.&nbsp;
		                </div></div><div class="one-card1__link"><a class="one-btn one-btn--link one-btn--bare one-btn--icon one-btn--icon-before one-u-text-left" href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/optical-transport-network/" aria-disabled="false"><span class="one-btn__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="svg-pictogram svg-pictogram--arrow-right" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="M31 .4L19.4 12l38 38-38 38L31 99.6 80.6 50 31 .4zm0 0"/></svg></span><span class="one-btn__label">Lees meer</span></a></div></div></div></div><div class="one-grid1__cell"><div id="block-40017" class="one-card1 one-panel block content--full-height one-u-color-base one-card1--has-subtitle one-panel--shadow one-panel--border"
    ><style>
            #block-40017-card-hero-image .one-card-hero-image__image {
            background-image: url('https://i.tb-content.net/cms/1d38cb/2024-overig/cloud1.png');
        }
    
    </style><figure
    class="one-card-hero-image one-card-hero-image--lg one-card-hero-image--for-panel"
    role="img"
    id="block-40017-card-hero-image" aria-hidden="true"><a
                        href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/multicloud/"
                        tabindex="-1"
                            class="one-card-hero-image__image one-card-hero-image__scalable"
    

                                                ><span class="one-u-sr-only">Artikel</span></a><div class="one-btn one-btn--primary one-btn--square one-btn--sm one-card-hero-image__continue-button"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="svg-pictogram svg-pictogram--arrow-right-straight" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="m50 100 50-50L50 0 39.879 9.97l32.78 32.93H0v14.2h72.659l-32.78 32.779z" fill-rule="evenodd"/></svg></div></figure><div class="one-card1__wrapper"><div class="one-card1__top"><div id="block-40017_one-media-header" class="one-media-header one-card1__header one-u-m-b-8 one-media-header--icon-sm one-media-header--title-sm one-media-header--title-normal one-media-header--subtitle-md"><div class="one-media-header__body"><header><a
                            href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/multicloud/"
                            class="one-media-header__heading-link"

                            
                            
                                                    ><h4 class="one-media-header__title one-media-header__title--color-black"><h3>Artikel</h3></h4></a><div class="one-media-header__subtitle one-u-m-b-0"><h2>Multicloud: wat is het en hoe zet je het slim in?<h2></div></header></div></div><div class="one-card1__content">
                    			Multicloud biedt flexibiliteit en tal van andere voordelen voor je IT-infrastructuur. Maar hoe zorg je dat je het maximale uit deze aanpak haalt zonder verdwaald te raken in complexiteit? In dit uitgebreide artikel duiken we in wat multicloud precies inhoudt, welke voordelen het biedt, wat de grootste uitdagingen zijn bij een multicloud omgeving en hoe je een succesvolle multicloud strategie implementeert die bijdraagt aan jouw bedrijfsdoelstellingen.&nbsp;
		                </div></div><div class="one-card1__link"><a class="one-btn one-btn--link one-btn--bare one-btn--icon one-btn--icon-before one-u-text-left" href="https://signetbreedband.nl/ons-werk/artikelen/multicloud/" aria-disabled="false"><span class="one-btn__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="svg-pictogram svg-pictogram--arrow-right" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="M31 .4L19.4 12l38 38-38 38L31 99.6 80.6 50 31 .4zm0 0"/></svg></span><span class="one-btn__label">Lees meer</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><style>
                        
